{"tid":1396260,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【中共建軍節】梁競徽獲封「愛国藝人」   中国藝人紛紛道賀","createTime":"2019-08-02T04:43:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T11:03:03.000Z","uid":184679,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"9a8d87ad8ee7131218b29ebfdb43701a07508da8","tid":1396260,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T04:43:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.modia.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/5d42a3acbf202.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.modia.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F08%2F5d42a3acbf202.jpeg&h=bd15b16f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n8月1日，今天除了是8號風波旭日之外，原來還是內地的「中國建軍節」！藝各領導之外，一班血濃於水的愛國藝人亦分別在微博表達愛國言詞，同為解放軍紀念日道賀。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modia.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/1564639981_09d4_5d42a3a7bb166.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.modia.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F08%2F1564639981_09d4_5d42a3a7bb166.jpg&h=dc16d36d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其中梁競徽 （前名：梁烈唯），以及鍾鎮濤、惠州市政協委員陳小春、Angelababy、洪天明、呂頌賢等等，原來都有為解放軍致敬。內地網民更封梁競徽 （唯唯）為「愛國藝人」。<br />\n<br />\n在微博擁逾220萬粉絲的梁競徽今日就在微博貼紅底白字「81」，留言：「在這個特別的日子，送上特別的敬意」並附了加油的公仔打氣，獲大陸網民一面倒勁讚：「香港現在的局面，你還能公開支持解放軍，年輕人典範」、「你這樣三觀正的藝人，才是香港未來的希望，加油！」、「唯唯超棒！祖國和你都會更好！」、「現在香港鬧翻天，港警都朝天開槍了，你還敢支持81解放軍，唯唯愛國藝人。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.modia.com.hk/2019/08/01/136513/%E3%80%90%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%BB%BA%E8%BB%8D%E7%AF%80%E3%80%91%E6%A2%81%E7%AB%B6%E5%BE%BD%E7%8D%B2%E5%B0%81%E3%80%8C%E6%84%9B%E5%9C%8B%E8%97%9D%E4%BA%BA%E3%80%8D%EF%BC%81%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E8%97%9D/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.modia.com.hk%2F2019%2F08%2F01%2F136513%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E8%25BB%258D%25E7%25AF%2580%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%25A2%2581%25E7%25AB%25B6%25E5%25BE%25BD%25E7%258D%25B2%25E5%25B0%2581%25E3%2580%258C%25E6%2584%259B%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%2597%259D%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E3%2580%258D%25EF%25BC%2581%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%